OL,3,CReform councillor investigated over
OL,4,Cpolling station ice creams
OL,6,FThe former deputy leader of
OL,7,FLeicestershire County Council is under
OL,8,Fpolice investigation over allegations
OL,9,Fhe tried to influence voters by giving
OL,10,Fout ice creams outside a polling
OL,11,Fstation during May's local elections.
OL,13,FThe 22-year-old, who left both his
OL,14,Fdeputy leader and adult social care
OL,15,Fcabinet role last month, was filmed in
OL,16,FMay this year allegedly handing out
OL,17,Fice creams during his and Reform UK's
OL,18,Flocal election campaign in North West
OL,19,FLeicestershire.
