OL,3,CReform councillor investigated over
OL,4,Cpolling station ice creams
OL,6,FThe ice cream van is reportedly family-
OL,7,Fowned, with Leicestershire Police
OL,8,Fconfirming it had received a third-
OL,9,Fparty report about the van's proximity
OL,10,Fto the polling station.
OL,12,FA police spokesperson said officers
OL,13,Fare now assessing whether the incident
OL,14,Fconstitutes being treated under
OL,15,Felectoral malpractice laws.
OL,17,FPolice said the report came from a
OL,18,Fwitness who reportedly saw the ice
OL,19,Fcream van outside the polling station.
