OL,3,CReform councillor investigated over
OL,4,Cpolling station ice creams
OL,6,FA police spokesperson said: "The force
OL,7,Freceived a report from a third party
OL,8,Fof an ice cream van outside a polling
OL,9,Fstation in May 2025. This is being
OL,10,Fassessed as to whether this
OL,11,Fconstitutes treating under electoral
OL,12,Fmalpractice."
OL,14,FAccording to the Electoral Commission,
OL,15,Funder electoral law, an offence is
OL,16,Fcommitted if someone gives or provides
OL,17,Fany meat, drink, entertainment or
OL,18,Fprovision to any person for the
OL,19,Fpurpose of influencing that person to
OL,20,Fvote or refrain from voting.
